{"tid":1434202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我噚晚發咗個夢","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T14:01:07.000Z","uid":23094,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5a3e2283af7709fe33350c5eda3106e5062fe5","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"我夢見條柒婆終於跪低<br />\n開記者會宣佈五大訴求，一個不漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式用「撤回」呢兩個字宣佈取消修例，承諾永不重推<br />\n仲承諾喺任期內會重啟政改，任期完結前實行真普選<br />\n下一任特首將會係一人一票選出嚟<br />\n仲同台灣達成協議移交陳同佳<br />\n獨立調查委員會，撤銷義士控罪，撤銷暴動定性呢啲都唔使再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一聽完即刻掉低哂手頭上嘅嘢，飛的衝咗去煲底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到之後我見到有幾十萬個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n企滿咗煲底、煲外、添馬、夏愨道⋯⋯<br />\n現場十分和平，一隻狗都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後全場數咗5聲，一齊除口罩拋上天<br />\n然後同身邊嘅兄弟姊妹互相擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係咪都好期待呢一日？<br />\n係嘅話就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留住條命</span>一齊見證呢一日來臨<br />\n到時除口罩畀我睇下你個樣同埋攬下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.S. 發夢嘅嘢唔使咁認真</span>"},{"pid":"de3b553ae30e0e8fab7d5a3117a0efb5063968f3","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e757b0e9904174e0478a5372e196a7545705c6","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc893f9fc7449dfa4916e73fa575f6be67793c0a","tid":1434202,"uid":194358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:54:22.000Z","msg":"我都想有依一日"},{"pid":"d93c7b14981fb295554589c793b70216470dc100","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc893f9fc7449dfa4916e73fa575f6be67793c0a","tid":1434202,"uid":194358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:54:22.000Z","msg":"我都想有依一日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b82d25e3389072a135a9f313ad9672dd716d5e","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97ffbd38c64d4addcacc9348e2ec07a6c89b870","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"咪撚諗住自己一個就咁走咗去咁撚自私精呀"},{"pid":"f9cb22c30134cde8b3ef581edd71d1b9d26fa3db","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a26928d28c1c7daa4417fe92991af22ffb2828b","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37f173c62a7937ab714e3803c1e1f48b359c87f","tid":1434202,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}